                    </span>
                </li>
                <li class="tatt-about-company-numbers__item">
                    <span class="tatt-about-company-numbers__item-heading">
                        125 лет
                    </span>
                    <span class="tatt-about-company-numbers__item-text">
                        опыта работы в сфере телекоммуникационных услуг
                    </span>
                </li>
                <li class="tatt-about-company-numbers__item">
                    <span class="tatt-about-company-numbers__item-heading">
                        68 000 кв.км
                    </span>
                    <span class="tatt-about-company-numbers__item-text">
                        охват деятельностью
                    </span>
                </li>
                <li class="tatt-about-company-numbers__item">
                    <span class="tatt-about-company-numbers__item-heading">
                        более 650 000
                    </span>
                    <span class="tatt-about-company-numbers__item-text">
                        абонентов телефонии
                    </span>
                </li>
                <li class="tatt-about-company-numbers__item">
                    <span class="tatt-about-company-numbers__item-heading">
                        свыше 500 000
                    </span>
                    <span class="tatt-about-company-numbers__item-text">
