            </p>
            
            <a href="/" class="tatt-about-company__link">
                Узнать больше
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="tatt-about-company-head">
        <div class="gl__page-content tatt-about-company-head__content">
            <img src="img/tatt-about-page/head.jpg" alt="Фото директора">
